{"tid":2148631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有工程師批評內地助建臨時醫院是政治凌駕專業","createTime":"2020-08-10T04:33:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T07:26:31.000Z","uid":156254,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"183dd0f6b7ee99352da75a71466aeb58becba9f9","tid":2148631,"uid":156254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:33:53.000Z","msg":"本港將在中央協助下，在亞博館附近空地興建臨時醫院。有資深土木工程師認為，本港工程的建築標準、監管質素也比內地高，施工速度亦不會比內地遜色，過往是本地工程師到內地參建項目居多，批評政府今次邀請中央協助，是政治凌駕工程專業。<br />\n<br />\n有參與醫院工程多年的業界人士認為，本港工程界有能力組裝達國際水平的負壓病房，不過亦樂見中央提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542830-20200810.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542830-20200810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=43b7f33e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542830-20200810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=c33ff2fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542830-20200810.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"1c32a62ddf6175d83ae7796ec81ddaa6eb7c56cd","tid":2148631,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"訓左幾耐呀工程師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n高鐵 沙中線 港珠澳 三跑 有邊樣唔係"},{"pid":"b9c54951e9fed4428ca589ef3bec6e44f6203bf4","tid":2148631,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1c32a62ddf6175d83ae7796ec81ddaa6eb7c56cd","tid":2148631,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"訓左幾耐呀工程師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor